@node reg ShareWare
    @{u}@{b}How to register UCT@{ub}@{uu}

UCT is ShareWare and limited. The 'save project' and 'find' functions are disabled when unregistered.

Use the 'Register' program to fill the form out and email the form (do NOT edit by hand!) to <@{b}thomas.nordh@swipnet.se@{ub}>.
The registration fee is at least 50 SEK in CASH ONLY.
